race.comment: BUSH PROFIT (7) jumped well and stalked the lead before boxing on to finish second (22.58) at Warrnambool in Grade 5. Missed the frame only look here. Makes plenty of appeal. RELEASED (1) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (23.84) at Horsham behind Eat Your Spinach in a Grade 5. Led around the bend before fighting on well and should give a sight. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings five times from seven starts. Expected to be in the finish again. LOVE A BOURBSKI (6) missed the frame and safely held latest finishing 6th at this track following on from a win (24.30) at Bendigo the start prior. Form here at the trip sound including six wins. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Expected to run well. PAW JANELLE (2) is worth consideration.
